name: yin yang
description:
Yin and yang represent the opposite poles and contradictions of the world
 (Two opposing but complementary principles)
 Yin and Yang remind us that good and bad are an integral part of our lives, and the key to this harmony is to accept the positive and the negative together, not to take one part and throw away the other.
